Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.44,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I got all choked up at Harumi's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:07.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen her look so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:12.31,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,She said she was going on her honeymoon to have a baby right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:16.58,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m glad that she seemed so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I love wedding dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.98,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Weddings in churches are so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:29.91,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Over 100 people attended the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:33.75,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’ve never been to such a large wedding before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:39.93,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, when will I be as happy as Harumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:51.56,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It was a shame that, although there were many people at the wedding who knew each other, there weren’t many people for me to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.07,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,And Takeshi-san couldn’t come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.52,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Kanoko couldn’t, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.07,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I know that people living in a society like this have a lots of things they need to do, but I wish they'd make time to go to their friend’s wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:07.84,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.84,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:15.20,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’d want all my friends to attend my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:21.12,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I guess I really do want to get married.
